## Related Documentation

- **Voice System:** `${PAI_DIR}/voice-server/USAGE.md`
- **Agent Architecture:** `${PAI_DIR}/Skills/CORE/agent-protocols.md`
- **History/UOCS:** `${PAI_DIR}/Skills/CORE/history-system.md`
